And when it ſhall pleaſe GOD he comes home in ſafetie, will deſerve to bee received by all his Fathers Subjects lyk a bleſſing ſent from heaven. For there was never in any Prince of his Race, more Religion, underſtanding and good Nature, honeſtie and Activeneſſe, the LORD croune all with his long lyfe, and then is Our Yle happie.
